    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Word from root</title>
      <link>https://sanskrit-coders.github.io/grammar/word-from-root/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://sanskrit-coders.github.io/grammar/word-from-root/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;pratipadika-declension&#34;&gt;prAtipadika declension&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Produce declensions while showing sUtra-s (&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://lanover.com/lan/sanskrit/subanta.html&#34;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Inflected word generation is usually based on the &amp;lsquo;word and paradigm&amp;rsquo; model,  close to the work such as ruupa chandrikaa which gives the naamaruupaavalii for &amp;rsquo;typical&amp;rsquo; words ending in different var.nas in different lingas.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;(&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/work/fflex/index.html&#34;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://tdil-dc.in/san/skt_gen/generators.html&#34;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;=&lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.uohyd.ac.in/lang_tech/21st-oct/downloads.html&#34;&gt;H1&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.uohyd.ac.in/scl/ashtadhyayi_simulator/index.html&#34;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.uohyd.ac.in/scl/skt_gen/generators.html&#34;&gt;H2&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.inria.fr/DICO/grammar.html&#34;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit1.ccv.brown.edu/tomcat/sl/NominalMorphology&#34;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Apps (&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/113859883459735318216/posts/Bcv6wpT3qcA&#34;&gt;ViPra&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Limitation: However, as a generative model the above is not perfect because, not being based firmly on pANini&amp;rsquo;s rules (which separate saMskR^ita from apabhraMShA), they may generate wrong inflections.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;These can in-turn be used to analyze inflected words (&lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.uohyd.ac.in/Heritage/DICO/index.html#stemmer&#34;&gt;1F&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.inria.fr/DICO/index.html#stemmer&#34;&gt;2F&lt;/a&gt;, I=&lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.uohyd.ac.in/scl/morph/index.html&#34;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit1.ccv.brown.edu/tomcat/sl/FunderburkInterface?type=2&#34;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://sanskrit.jnu.ac.in/subanta/rsubanta.jsp&#34;&gt;Dl&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
